title: Badhuset
description: Set in the WWII era, the story tells of a boy in a small village who befriends three girls around his age. One day he discovers a young couple sneaking into an old and cracked bathing shack and decides to alert his new friends. When the kids join up at the shack, the eldest girl comes up with the idea to lock the couple inside, threatening not to let them out until they "do it" and allow the kids to watch from the outside. And so begins the psychological warfare...::Icelander

title: Brazil Carnival
description: It is a film about the carnival in Rio de Janeiro, with bodies that dance, talk and get excited. The city becomes a jungle and everything is allowed. It is an explicit carnival with penises and butts dancing with the rhythm of samba. It is a film that emphasizes the freedom of expression. Portraits the carnival as a kind of an orgy / a consented orgy, where you explore your desires and fantasies and be who you really are.::Antonio da Silva Films

title: Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.: Slingshot
description: Following Inhuman Yo-Yo Rodriguez also known as 'Slingshot' on a personal Mission against time.

title: Carne
description: After a dreadful incident coupled with an ungovernable paroxysm of violence, a butcher will fall into a downward spiral that will burn to the ground whatever dignity still remained in him.

title: Charlie Brown: Blockhead's Revenge
description: The cast of MTV's 'Teen Wolf' teams up with Funny or Die and gives Charlie Brown a spooky twist.

title: Last Night in Soho: Deleted Scenes
description: Deleted scenes cut from the film, 'Last Night in Soho'.

title: Dr. Quinn, Morphine Woman with Jane Seymour
description: Dr. Quinn is back! And her new show is nothing like the original!

title: Don't Hug Me I'm Scared 6
description: Now that Duck is gone as well, Yellow Guy is being tortured and mocked by a lamp who is trying to teach him about dreams. Meanwhile, Red Guy discovers the truth about their show.

title: Night and Fog
description: The history of Nazi Germany's death camps of the Final Solution and the hellish world of dehumanization and death contained inside.

title: Perils in Nude Modeling
description: On the verge of expulsion, a hapless art student must decide between life-long ambition and love when an audacious nude model makes a dangerous demand in the middle of class.

title: Night of the Devil
description: It is the night before Halloween aka Devil's Night in1978 and four teens, Chris, Vivian, Davis, and Laurel enter the woods for some mischief but instead they come face to face with the Devil and a night of fun turns into a hellish experience.

title: Anima
description: In a short musical film directed by Paul Thomas Anderson, Thom Yorke of Radiohead scores and stars in a mind-bending visual piece. Best played loud.

title: Ice Age: Scrat Tales
description: Six all-new animated shorts starring Scrat, the hapless saber-toothed squirrel of the "Ice Age" adventures, who experiences the ups and downs of fatherhood.

title: Come Home
description: During the holiday season, Angie, a pack's mother, gets stranded by a blizzard and winds up backstage at the variety show studio. She then gets a chance to connect with her family even if she can't physically make it back to the house.

title: Pirelli Calendar 2010 (The Making of)
description: A Lengthy Behind-the-Scenes Look at Terry Richardson Shooting Naked Supermodels for the Pirelli Calendar.

title: Shower Boys
description: After a heated training match with the team, twelve-year-old Viggo and Noel go home to challenge each other's limits and masculinity. A sudden stop to an innocent game questions what a male friendship is allowed to be.

title: 2036: Nexus Dawn
description: Niander Wallace demonstrates the merits of a new type of Nexus to the LAPD.

title: The Adventures of Puss in Boots
description: The famous cat protects the city of San Lorenzo, a mythical land invisible to the outside world.

title: The Accomplice
description: Arriving home from a long business trip, Jerry discovers a number of urgent messages on his answering machine from his impulsive and inept friend, Randy. Much to his surprise, Jerry is now an unwilling participant in one of Randy's boneheaded schemes.

title: Chucky: Friends Forever
description: A cop tries to get the bottom of his co-workers death.

title: Mighty Ducks: The Animated Series
description: A team of humanoid duck ice hockey team/freedom fighters fight evil between games.

title: Turbo Charged Prelude to 2 Fast 2 Furious
description: Taking place after The Fast and The Furious, Brian O'Connor tries to evade the law, which leads up to the events of 2 Fast 2 Furious.

title: A Story Takes Flight
description: Gwyneth, Kate and Zoe experience different sides of Dubai. Everyone gets to discover the city's magic and surprises in their own way.

title: All of This Unreal Time
description: On a journey from darkness into light, a man explores his failings as a human being.

title: Firebase
description: While fighting the Vietnam war, both sides face a new kind of threat that neither of them were prepared for.

title: From Devil's Breath
description: From Academy Award®-winning filmmaker Orlando von Einsiedel (THE WHITE HELMETS, VIRUNGA) and producer Leonardo DiCaprio, FROM DEVIL'S BREATH tells the unlikely first-person story of two remarkable narratives that come crashing together; the extraordinary community of survivors of the deadly 2017 wildfires in Portugal, fighting to ensure what they've lived through can never happen again; and a revolutionary, world-changing scientific discovery which could help protect us all from the climate emergency.::Time Studios
